  <mods:abstract>Myrna Granowitz (as Meg Brockie) and Allen Majesky (as Angus McGuffie) performing in a non-dress rehearsal of Brigadoon, which was directed by Michael McHale. The play was presented by the Pitt Players and the University of Pittsburgh at the Stephen Foster Memorial May 12th through 14th during the 1956-1957 season. The Pitt Players were a student theatre club at the University of Pittsburgh that was active from 1916 to 1960.</mods:abstract>
